# exploration challenges

## Purpose

To create a site to explore in the next session.

### Procedure

- Choose the site type
- Choose inhabitant framework
- Choose types of inhabitants
- Generate rooms of interest
- Arrange rooms
- Add optional map features
- Stock rooms
- Establish wandering encounters
- Establish daily life
- Finalise map

